trans-unit.source: The Pkcs9ContentType class defines the type of the content of a CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: Klasa Pkcs9ContentType definiuje typ zawartości wiadomości CMS/PKCS #7.

trans-unit.source: A Pkcs9ContentType object will be automatically generated and placed in the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo.SignedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property whenever the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.SignedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property for the corresponding signer is not empty.
trans-unit.target: Obiekt Pkcs9ContentType zostanie automatycznie wygenerowany i umieszczane w <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo.SignedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Właściwości zawsze, gdy <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.SignedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Właściwość odpowiednie osoby podpisującej nie jest pusty.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.SignedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo.SignedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The Pkcs9ContentType constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9ContentType"></xref> class.
The ContentType property gets an <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"></xref> object that contains the content type.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera właściwość ContentType <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"> </xref> obiekt, który zawiera typ zawartości.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"></xref> object that contains the content type.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"> </xref> Obiekt, który zawiera typ zawartości.

trans-unit.source: This method replaces the current <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9ContentType> object with the specified <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData> object.
trans-unit.target: Ta metoda zastępuje bieżącego <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9ContentType>obiektu z określonym <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData>obiektu.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9ContentType>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData"></xref> object from which to copy information.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData"> </xref> Obiektu, z którego można skopiować informacje.
